    REST_API SERVICE PROJECT DEVELOPMENT PROCESS FOR CRUD OPERATION

1.Update db configs in application properties
2.create employee entity
3.create dao interface
4.create dao implementation
5.create a RESTController to use DAO


If you have using CRUD operation without need more code or instead of using DAO layer and boiler of codes, then you
simply using a Spring-Data=JPA. This is the Magic method and it gives CRUD operation free for you..

In order to using Spring-Data-JPA using CRUD operation, the developement process include,
steps
        1. Extend JpaRepository interface
        2. Use your Reposotory in your app

 JPA Repository provides the interface: JpaRepository
 Expose methods (some by inheritance from parents)